"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Meredith Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuo-fiUuSY1dqQcrQGAp8JiUxESlNJpmbOFMUJw463gxKuau8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My review is long overdue! I’ve been seeing Dr. Vo at 4th \u0026 Seneca Dental for almost a year now, and I can’t say enough good things about the care I’ve received. I’ve gone through Invisalign, a crown, a filling, and routine treatments — and every step of the way Dr. Vo has been thorough, kind, and highly skilled. The quality of his work is the best I’ve ever experienced compared to other dentists, and the results truly speak for themselves.\n\nThe office uses the latest technology, which makes treatments smoother, more comfortable, and incredibly precise.\n\nThe whole team makes you feel at ease the moment you walk in. Nikki at the front desk always greets you by name and makes scheduling a breeze. The dental assistants are wonderful, and of course Bradley, the office dog, is absolutely adorable.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dentist who truly cares, delivers exceptional results, and runs a modern, welcoming practice, I can’t recommend Dr. Vo and his team enough!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0MAeWtb0vyJuohYT__wJ4apj6WTDgMbOTJgRXROBUu4r7wiUPFAGXWEjZNY5JfizC4pkcRcSd2qoRLo3BzSDIlhlfFIrrExwS4cDj6ucqf7cO1LkO9tZ-pQAPI3EzQEeC8-wevWMjJDd_E=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2fqa_I1gICn1kZztb8leFRyFFKH7kHAhxqdX0KpDuN_EJFKNJVzZMiH00f3ZU7C2o7Ogj_W8iY82EDuib0Lwevbz-_pTXTA4E4TMwSuyHP0OiDzWXG0OWg1n8J307w2p-LbELRCc2GAo8=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-2"},{"Name":"Darlene Kline","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmb7l31VEtUeAyrYG8J_Er28cHmshKYYifN2u25lQsOBsE1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Dr. John’s for the past three years, and I truly cannot say enough wonderful things about him and his team. Not only is he an excellent dentist, but he also has the very best bedside manner — calm, kind, and reassuring.\n\nAnd then there’s Bradley — his beloved dog — who is actually in the office, wagging his tail and ready to be your personal dental support doggy. He adds such a warm, comforting presence that instantly puts you at ease.\n\nNikki, the office manager, always takes the time to ask about my family. She genuinely cares, and it shows. The entire staff is made up of the most pleasant, compassionate people. Their kindness isn’t forced — it’s simply who they are.\n\nI actually look forward to going to the dentist because I know I will be welcomed, cared for, and treated with dignity and respect every single time.\n\nWho knew going to the dentist could feel this good? 😂🤷🏻‍♀️🥰","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-WQAjUsIAz8hDsoMxEwMGnwf49wXAu6O8pt8Ax8pi78i8ezGq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Jon and his staff are some of the best in the dental business. I’ve never been to a more modern and more client centric dentist in my life. My aunt was my dental hygienist for most of my life, so I went where she was, and I never had complaints when I lived in Texas. But man, I may have gone elsewhere if I had known a place like this existed. They are really kind and knowledgeable, with the some of the most advanced technology I’ve experienced. Check them out, and you will not be disappointed. I was going to another office in south Seattle because it was closer, but this place is worth the commute. Just wow!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brianna Wendt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZyFu2Nhv45dD7e7DSaKK36emLR4L16gmifr_gm32IE6Ph5KGs0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would give more than five stars if I could. I have been seeing the team at 4th and Seneca for many years now. Dr. Vo did beautiful composite veneers on my uppers a few years ago to address discoloration from lifelong GERD and he and the team are the only people I trust with my teeth moving forward. I have now moved across the country and I fly back to Seattle to see Dr. Vo.  No joke! Amazing cosmetic dentistry work, incredible staff, and Nikki at the front desk is awesome. They work with tough schedules and always make sure you feel great about the results.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Coleman Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUHREPJuvbtmRJegKVORLNEWav__6tJh9IQzY2MJUVm-fyTj8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their entire team is amazing from the front counter to Doctor Jon. First, I wanna say Nikki is one of the best front receptionist ever very likable very personable and honestly amazing at her job. She does a great job at keeping the chaos of the business together for her team and their customers. I’m a little biased on this one, but my personal friend and favorite orthodontist I’ve ever had. Frank is also very very good at his job. Very kind very understanding. Great communication. Frank is definitely a star of a genuine person in the dental industry here in Washington. And Dr. Jon is one of the best dentist I’ve ever had the pleasure of being in my teeth’s corner! 😁🦷🪥 when I asked Dr. John the first time we met if he could answer some hard, maybe even not beneficial to his business questions about my teeth health. He was more than happy to educate me and give me good resources to educate myself. Couldn’t appreciate their entire team service more probably in the top five best dental practices in Washington state. Parking is even accommodated through the Seattle library right across the street. 100 out of 10!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nick Lozzi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzP5HgxN-Olvd-EqAVFJPPB6eoa5vcgBg5SYlMj9kf1lskAEz2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to 4th \u0026 Seneca Dental today and it was honestly the best experience I’ve had at a dentist. Every staff member was friendly, honest, and took the time to clearly explain everything that was going on. It had been over five years since I’d seen a dentist because my last experience in Seattle wasn’t great and I was quoted way too high for the same work I needed, so I’m really glad I got a second opinion. I did a lot of research before choosing them and I’m very happy with that decision. I have dental insurance and the prices they quoted were fair and accurate. Dr. Vo was very nice and straightforward, which I really appreciated. I wouldn’t choose another dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gordon Ledingham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU97Axa2Q6Q6jwhTdL3svWzHRgL1ynWxm68XHqH1kUAa8jQ5Q_Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Vo \u0026 team are amazing. He’s is a dental artist, informed, caring and qualified and delivering quality, fine-tuned dentistry.. I am always in good hands with them (and my own father was a renowned, highly respected dentist). I can trust Dr. Vo and his staff and associates. I fly to Seattle just for his excellent care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grace Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvNXi-SL2mVchhW8jwQrhvCH4ZRPvArh1fwLyexGV4Zr55I-c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been coming to this dental office for over six years, and I’ve always had a great experience. The staff are consistently friendly and welcoming. My dental cleaner, Frank, always does an excellent job and is thorough and professional. The doctor monitors my teeth closely and gives clear, helpful advice too. I feel well taken care of here and would definitely recommend this office.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
{"input_id":"4985f8da-4737-4e98-ba46-d0d63c0325fb","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/place/3rd+%26+Columbia+Dental+Seattle/data=!4m7!3m6!1s0x54906ab13ce5a1db:0xfcb67014ad4b6e49!8m2!3d47.6046295!4d-122.3328247!16s%2Fg%2F1w2ytlm6!19sChIJ26HlPLFqkFQRSW5LrRRwtvw?authuser=0\u0026hl=en\u0026rclk=1","cid":"18209865377428237897","title":"3rd \u0026 Columbia Dental Seattle","categories":["Dentist","Cosmetic dentist","Dental clinic","Dental hygienist","Dental implants periodontist","Dental implants provider","Emergency dental service","Endodontist","Teeth whitening service"],"category":"Dentist","address":"810 3rd Ave #200, Seattle, WA 98104","open_hours":{"Friday":["Closed"],"Monday":["8 AM–4 PM"],"Saturday":["Closed"],"Sunday":["Closed"],"Thursday":["8 AM–4 PM"],"Tuesday":["8 AM–4 PM"],"Wednesday":["8 AM–4 PM"]},"popular_times":{},"web_site":"https://3rdandcolumbiadental.com/?utm_source=GMBListing\u0026utm_medium=Organic","phone":"(206) 219-2587","plus_code":"JM38+VV Seattle, Washington","review_count":261,"review_rating":4.9,"reviews_per_rating":{"1":4,"2":2,"3":1,"4":6,"5":248},"latitude":47.604629499999994,"longtitude":-122.33282469999999,"status":"","description":"","reviews_link":"","thumbnail":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEVX_ncMJyQd86oBW9ipGV4seuZKf1g3KLVZAlAJbDQJb4BUt2S0E-smvdE3RxFo97Hlv2YHKmBbbsTqU3cRn9SmE47C7u0eYqSkq0dQHZX7gXn2ryVTID2Bre4iQExojBxGKY=w408-h544-k-no","timezone":"America/Los_Angeles","price_range":"","data_id":"0x54906ab13ce5a1db:0xfcb67014ad4b6e49","place_id":"ChIJ26HlPLFqkFQRSW5LrRRwtvw","images":[{"title":"All","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEVX_ncMJyQd86oBW9ipGV4seuZKf1g3KLVZAlAJbDQJb4BUt2S0E-smvdE3RxFo97Hlv2YHKmBbbsTqU3cRn9SmE47C7u0eYqSkq0dQHZX7gXn2ryVTID2Bre4iQExojBxGKY=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFiAXoyh7h8H3yf-veY3qvmlnG7AgtBw2SeS-Gz-82JwOnJZGGqilKgwFEBZs423Yd8MfxN_uAzxDNekEF2vNjUHZ74jlW1XKFZPEVSm8v-vgpPH1bmwp4AKnUxUQf29X7WYys7=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=PAufZehgU3DzG2U0b2dAHw\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=49.349945\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://3rdandcolumbiadental.com/book-an-appointment/?utm_source=GMBListing\u0026utm_medium=Organic","source":"3rdandcolumbiadental.com"}],"menu":{"link":"/url?q=https://3rdandcolumbiadental.com/%3Futm_source%3DGMBListing%26utm_medium%3DOrganic\u0026opi=79508299\u0026sa=U\u0026ved=0ahUKEwit4uKtur-UAxX9LUQIHbsmEqMQqRkIHSgQ\u0026usg=AOvVaw3pRwrbE9z88zMofyNK0BXx","source":"3rdandcolumbiadental.com"},"owner":{"id":"117247482903840529077","name":"3rd \u0026 Columbia Dental Seattle (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117247482903840529077"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Central Business District","street":"810 3rd Ave #200","city":"Seattle","postal_code":"98104","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Yubin Song","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVrYPlmlkZSoFgSGiuvHvLFVUONf-QG94kW7_RBm8F0jt3ocIEbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are an adult patient who is considering to get a Invisalign for the teeth you've been thinking about for your entire life, I highly recommend 3rd and Columbia Dental. As an adult starting a ortho treatment for the first time, I was initially nervous about the process but Dr. Park was very attentive and took time to come up with the plan that will address my concerns so I decided to start the treatment. My two main concerns were crowded lower anterior teeth and narrow upper jaw. Before starting the treatment, Dr. Park clearly explained the treatment plan, timeline, expected results. Their dental assistances are also experienced and knowledgeable. My attachments barely came off during the whole process. Even as a first time ortho patient, I felt the treatment plan was well thought out, precisely moving my teeth without causing excessive pain. I'm currently done with my initial treatment and waiting for refinements sets but I'm already very happy with the results so far. My teeth are more straight and my facial asymmetry is improved. I'm breathing better because my upper jaw was expanded more. Do your research and get a consultation but I really think it's not too late to get your teeth fixed in your 30's.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2h15SYs9nqPt65HWfK5Xed4ejORfuSnlTzjQOxgwIEWtjv67zMRPP4pi7N0CiJ8z-JUHQEeDWoIXjBNhKBwhK8H2zSV3ETqsVzg3s4RgUt-zIVfG9N6Ngi7grFagNjSZTpqe8AqzZulSxE=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-12"},{"Name":"Jayanth Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfSXt5VLuD3Hpkpq5aU4qAZH7zq6WWA004ldAmauO27ian_Yf7yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellently run operation. From the Front-desk onwards, I had friendly smiling faces welcome me, and usher me in through the various steps that were required. The hygenist, Grace is exceptionally professional and patient. I haven't been to the dentist in a couple of years, post covid, and she took her time to do a tremendous job in cleaning my teeth.\n\nThe doctor was friendly, paid close attention to all my information that i had shared prior to visit, and was very friendly, attentive, and knowledgeable, in helping me understand my options. I got so lucky picking this spot. They're super good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gabby S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhkBfpR0ZfISI3z4Jzds82v2ivTL-pYgkm83HbiTXv0F1X7rN1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really awesome practice. The hygienist are nice, gentle with the cleaning, and walk you through with what they are doing. Dr. Park is so kind and explains things in a digestible way. The office staff is friendly and helpful too. Would definitely recommend this practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Asia Larkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdWVkgPQtNGXPu2gfmCRosotxujnPjI3kXEVvTDPlBzMVCrZXNUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team here is great. They keep you informed along every step. They were super proactive in communication and very friendly in office. As a new patient getting set up can be overwhelming but they made the whole process smooth. I left feeling confident about the work they did and appreciate the care they provided.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve \u0026 Gwen Cover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjEY4wlniFF9Z4zCH6udnX4U1xR1bvlI5wT_uKPuw6PenvMV4H=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited this office with an emergency while on travel. From my first call to Christine, I was seen within an hour. The appointment was on-time, smooth, and a great experience.  The doctor and team were very understanding of my situation and had me in and out so I could make a critical flight connection.  Thank you for being so kind.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittany Bennett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUINsl5ep8d032-fGRoqAx_FERHMF7p7tkdQXM8boaXOzNHiC4RIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Park and the team were great. Kind, thorough, and accommodating. They fixed my chipped front tooth after my exam even though I wasn’t scheduled for it, and it turned out beautiful!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Fischer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9SegaGemdtgVpya87mC85HTJyqFDbBJP1qJIY3SgWgr2Rrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been to 3rd and Columbia dental more times in the last two years than I would like to count... my teeth :(  (cavities, cracked teeth, crown(s), cleaning) but every step of the way it has been an enjoyable experience!\nFrom walking into the office and immediately being greeted by the front desk staff, to a prompt check in and intake, taking your annual x-rays,  the procession of walking you to your chair (each space is pretty sectioned off so its like your own room). I've come to know a lot of the staff I normally see on a first name basis (heyyyy!), chairs are comfy, you get cute terminator glasses (see attached photo), a bib, and you're off to whatever you need to do.\nDr. David Park is just beyond, a professional and very sweet man.  Efficient, honest, and it's all just so easy. I have fallen asleep and laughed here more times than I would like to count with my mouth WIDE open.\nAnyways, just go, your teeth will thank you. Use your insurance, the dentist (especially when you look into the eyes of this one) isn't scary, and we all swoon for a beautiful smile.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3cdhA9e-4za1YQYEv3NfG2PlkLWPXjCtguXzHPuSWjflrbiTeZSkz4vv0G-YaaF49afiDnOXz5Az3GvmLnjVrEA2XDyoSiOAvt3moLTnsYa2XCP-D6-jLZ4e5Avgc9nXXRXu9JqqU1FjLj=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-30"},{"Name":"Joonhyuk Yun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYeXjXjKFz8HNOE5w33ba3PZn073n007vEcknp7BZ_GhyVAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The doctor and assistant were so kind and friendly! The doctor did a thorough dental exam but kept it quick and efficient.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
