Choi was not going to be in the Seattle office but he reprioritized his schedules to drop by to accommodate my need.  When I got there 15 minutes before my appointment time, Dr. Choi was already there, and he started seeing me right away.  After attending to my main issue, he even helped me clean my teeth and removed stains.  Dr. Choi listens to my concerns and responses in a caring and personable manner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jae Yoo (fkkcloud)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5Le2OQEPagdaBWIeAgx3XkiTem23shfdTNaRebqLMEJfQoz7U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Cornerstone for a dental check-up, and I was thoroughly impressed. The clinic was immaculately clean, which immediately put me at ease. Throughout the appointment, the dentist was very careful and attentive to my needs. They explained everything clearly and were incredibly kind throughout the entire process. I highly recommend for anyone in need of dental care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2qcuGkFmjoEboC-CiDhx-3OyOatrSTQiZIM5O7aJCS0SjV5KrAGnaU1f6VxiZXBi8qu43IdeYtFx8rmOOPBgLtMKoK23ruWSQUPDawoID_-8ImHLR2IF5CNfP3QKJbHaz2G7VS=k-no"],"When":"2024-6-4"},{"Name":"Chris Huffman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzIPV3HYRc3DGQWfWQjay2x9mJoVc4HFWVhv9cnO5TmUQeqcCx9A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I had a cleaning today and I have never left an appointment more soaked. Water was spraying directly in my face and updated my nose multiple times. There has to be a way to clean teeth without drenching the patient like they’re in a car wash.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alejandra Enriquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjvIi9l7wpOsNWRbCDsZdNoMujRXKp0chZrAfqGqL4o-Cq69g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone on the team that I’ve spoken with is incredibly kind, professional, and attentive. Dr. An is the best! She has been very supportive in making the best decision to address my dental needs. Parking is accessible via a garage behind One Union. I cannot recommend enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leah Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIK4nfb03tS4tAZ7_yez6mdn1tsZliY0_wQcVxY9Xh9tOAQ_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Ahn, Wallace, Bernice, and the receptionist were all amazing. Dr Ahn was so patient and careful. Very mindful of my fear of needles and numbing when at the dentist, she made sure I was okay every step of the way. I felt very safe and secure with everything we did - the deep cleaning, numbing, and putting in my crown. I would recommend Cornerstone Dental, specifially Dr Ahn, to anyone looking for a dentist in the Seattle area. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edward Nelson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4ryL6ClGONNDNIdlTqBP3rDyZyfmpCAFjealEBVCiEAnzLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hadn’t been to a dentist in a long time cause I hate going but finally made myself go after having some tooth pain. Found a local dentist office with good reviews and they got me in the next day. The staff was super nice and didn’t make me feel bad for waiting so long. The dentist was chill and explained everything before poking around. Turns out I had a cavity that needed to be filled. He showed me the X ray and walked through the options. The filling didn’t hurt like I thought it would and they used something that matched my tooth color. It took maybe 30 minutes and I was out of there. Only thing that bugged me was waiting a bit even with an appointment but whatever. My tooth feels better now and I’m glad I finally went. I already scheduled my next cleaning which is something I never do. If you’re nervous about the dentist like me give this place a try. They didn’t rush and treated me like a person not just a number. It actually wasn’t bad at all.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
