e},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Regina McCoy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4WalMZaUImsZxFwNWmBXk4L3k1uQI556DWswC-CASgTZSabTp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Park is the best dentist I’ve ever had in my life! My teeth have never been better since going here. The office management team is attentive and they have super flexible hours. I was able to get my whole cleaning done by 7:40 am! Love it here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"StMt MC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8qSKvCG8aottMwO-2rr6N93X0Hv0RLLSurld5S2hj9mrILg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent in every way. Today was my first visit. All “paperwork” was completed via text which is super easy. Knowledgeable and helpful staff. Long term teeth health discussed and costs explained. Could not be any better. Stuart C. Deep cleaning was super easy even after years of not going to the dentist. Probably saved my teeth!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mohamed El Neklawy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBgvNeTEK_TwMH8Q-NUuVqnYAhr-59fMwifhs6Y8bvAW-yhw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’d avoid this clinic if i were you.\n\nHere is my experience, I called ahead for a very simple procedure, reattaching a veneer that fell off. I was clearly quoted $206 on the phone. Another clinic quoted me $260, so I chose this one based on that price.\n\nWhen I arrived, they asked for payment right away. Then mid-procedure, I was told I had to pay an extra $160 with no prior warning and nothing changed they will cement and cure it, i asked on the phone “that’s for the whole procedure” and the lady on the phone said yes. When I explained that their receptionist said the service was included, they denied it. I asked them to pull the call recording, they disappeared for about 10 minutes, then came back and refused to provide it. I do admit \u0026 acknowledge tho that the receptionist I talked to on the phone was very nice.\n\nHowever, at that point, I was put in a position where I had no choice but to pay.\n\nTo be fair, the doctor was nice and did a good job. This issue is entirely with how the front desk handled pricing and communication of it.!I genuinely felt misled and taken advantage of, especially as a visitor to Seattle.\n\nVery disappointing experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karissa Vongkhamchanh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfnm3k-uh0LCl95USSybUKUosMYtsjortMHBK5jzXKzSDSOGP50w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I scheduled cleanings here because of the high reviews but unfortunately I haven’t been satisfied with my visits. I had a few fillings and the work was rushed. Both fillings were done in \u003c 20 minutes. I had to come back on another occasion because I couldn’t floss in between the new fillings. A testament that the work was rushed and not done well. On another occasion, the dental hygienist simply talks at you about what is wrong while listing a number of things that you are possibly doing contributing to the issue. They don’t ask what your routine is or how to help solve an issue pertinent to you so it feels like scolding and is just not very kind. Also, a heads up that parking is not free or covered by the office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sophia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhQJ-dY0QLdcuBmARdryeqYZzaZxboXUv3Shd7BTTfyIiZrA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a lovely staff! Thorough, yet quick and kind. It helps to have a wonderful view of Mount Rainier. So happy this is my new Dental crew!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0jHyCx0At9GZ3i34Bf-lRP01k93LdqYhx_lN8S-gar2UClUKN94LtAyYzdM9o7qUanmSOM7n083lP5XFkWODgxr8oBl0gPb2uZXY7A2jlSP3ppDQxU5FZgxkcvRLA-kQxIY7D_=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-31"},{"Name":"Pratik Nagelia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWu_7jDANIs6zgNxJBBGKV3wK18CPvmmRZEsG64Xz6Tk4HowA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best dental checkup I have had in US. The hygienist and doctors were super sweet and super knowledgeable. The scanning devices were top notch showing of deep scans of entire teeth structure. Definitely recommend visiting here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Drew Blyth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIt1vsuHbcnAhTLUqnXRHAfz2JGAZIhIm1n-oRQJxmkYCgYdw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lively atmosphere. Brightly lit, friendly staff, up beat music playing. Clean and modern. Staff did a great job cleaning while limiting discomfort. Will continue use First Hill Dental Center","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deepak Nair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUDP2HWG7Al1MAzSF78KqUql5Np_wK2nMDEpFqQrBMX43vj9Dz-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The first few visits were excellent. Dr. Singh replaced my crown and handled everything smoothly. Unfortunately, the service started declining after that. Even though I specifically requested to continue seeing Dr. Singh, I was assigned a different doctor at nearly every visit. On one occasion, I had a tongue injury the day before a cleaning appointment, and they refused to reschedule without charging an $85 fee since it was within 24 hours. I also had a very unpleasant cleaning where I left with multiple cuts in my mouth. To make matters worse, the newer doctors began recommending treatments that felt unnecessary; so much so that even the hygienist once advised me to disregard what the doctor had suggested, which I agreed with. It’s disappointing to see the quality decline so much over the past couple of years. I’ve since moved on to another dentist.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
