EppLUAiriKXnR6c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My mom is in a group home and needed a mobile check up and cleaning. They were very responsive and helpful at getting my mom scheduled quickly. Dr Kashi was delightful and very gentle with my mom. My mom kept saying \"he was really good\". He also spoke with her caregivers afterwards giving them some ideas of changes to her daily care routine necessary for her dental health. We are very happy with the services she received.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda Marra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3TmG5TDIDr2wO6qKJyG0-ez-uFrFEkWfLvzbwYEhlKPYxtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I feel like I've discovered my own private dentist who is compassionate and skilled to handle any issues I may have with my teeth. Rather than sitting uncomfortably in a tacky, crowded waiting room with bad music and too many people, it's a very private experience in a lovely environment on the 6th floor with a most commanding view. I trust Dr. Kashi completely, and I'm relieved I found him.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leslie Rhodes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-U4a6cG2b1X8rpKOT-xtsgzkfCAwBMTsOIydqg_eSaZEoxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were amazing!  I have severe anxiety and had a dental emergency which required extracting several teeth. I was able to have this done with out being sedated or even using nitrous oxide. They were so kind and gentle I will continue to go back for all my dental needs. They took time to go over financial options for me prior to my surgery so I knew what to expect. Can’t say enough good things about the doctor and his staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcUUaGDk6a-fjhZ5Cu-XIPavL5fBwet7DGNg-zqtNBa41XEw1mWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Kashi listened to me and provided me with options. He answered all my questions and worked with me to create a treatment plan best suited for me. He is patient and kind while still being honest and I recommend him to everyone. If you don't feel heard with your dentist, make the switch to Dr. Kashi - you won't regret it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anthony Tavera (NotAnthonyX)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbP-XQU_x2p-OCPgcFfARLArOg87AnndP6zRj-jpxwx7gZarc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had small an emergency with the worst timing- Dr. Kashi was able to see me in short notice, he was very kind and understanding! Thankfully we were able to identify and resolve the problem. I picked up the prescribed medication the next day from the nearest pharmacy, and Dr. Kashi even personally called the pharmacist to verify the prescription when delays came up. All before we had to make it to the docks that day for a cruise. Definition of a lifesaver- next time we visit Seattle, we’re stopping by to say hello!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria Bottles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4AW6pWmzks1aWKVRg7UwXo5OfmvWOpE3bc5UAbRjBZIH9jQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Kashi is great! Very personable.Always on time and very accommodating when you have an emergency. I trust him and his recommendations about my dental health completely","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"neiI lima","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLK5EbOjJNk8YlyeAAOpL1f6KN0bpO9wpUvFWZyAmSQDPN_Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Kashi is a very experienced and skilled dentist. He is a top notch dentist with great chairside manner and exhibits  excellent professional demeanor. I would highly recommend him to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Ferro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKS7fOiCg-Zn1jt7v53ZWfpRuZVcQFHw4luasJPh9vUvEuKow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The whole experience was unbelievably. The doctor was Warm and friendly. Made me feel comfortable. Before i knew it he was done and had the tooth out. I recommend this dentistry to everyone","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
