//lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoXaGaQO0gmFWYpwBwHusdwnRkB6GLBI2tQvMGtilTZztyiXiVxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Before going to this dentist, my teeth were completely fine and didn't give me any pain. After the two visits (and three extra appointments spent adjusting the fillings they gave me) I had last year, I still experience pain from their treatment to the point where I can't chew with half of my mouth. They will tell you they've found issues that no other dentist has and make you feel like you can trust them, but be cautious and get a second opinion when you feel it's too much, too fast. I strongly recommend looking elsewhere for a dentist and listening to the other folks who have left one star reviews.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"-","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRHPpEqx3phF7nuQ5Cja1shzgKfDYNocnYhhrGmjG3KnSgqnqe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hadn't been to the dentist in a very long time, and they were amazing about getting my oral health back on track and educating me on the \"whys\" behind everything.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erika Lane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWE_CD9Ui_AnjimKVzEUkcO3ARLl3nec6LcY5JPxp57QRJQbRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Larhs and everyone at Advanced Dentistry are wonderful. They always make sure I’m not in pain, and my teeth and gums are in good care with them. Best dental experience I’ve ever had.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paul McLain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8dMT3Bd_mCU1c94VqkoFUMlgxCpET1B6IJstOWyFdn3cIK2Vd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Larhs and her team are excellent.  They are both technically advanced and very customer focused. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria Sol Flaherty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5MGn-I-hZzQjr72iEzaGjAGkN04l9O_yRgR0yMzjTtnscAg=s120-